HEADWORD: hipline
<hw>hipline</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the line formed by
measuring the hip at its greatest part.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the line formed by the lower edge of hiplength
garment.</def>⟦br⟧
